@startuml
title
<size:16><b>UC-04: List a Product - Activity Diagram</b></size>
end title

|Seller|
start

:Navigate to Seller Dashboard and click 'Add New Listing';

|System|
:Display product listing form;

|Seller|
:Enter product details (title, category, sub-category, brand, model, condition, price, stock, description, specifications);

:Upload product images (1 to 8, JPEG/PNG, max 5MB each);

|System|
:Validate all required fields and image constraints;

if (All images valid?) then (no)
  :Display inline error for invalid image(s);
  :Seller re-uploads corrected images;
  note right: Alternative Flow 2 (loop back)
  --> :Upload product images;
else (yes)
endif

if (Seller wants to save as Draft?) then (yes)
  :Save listing as Draft (not submitted, visible only to Seller);
  stop
else (no)
endif

|Seller|
:Click 'Submit for Review';

|System|
:Save listing with status 'Pending Review' and upload images to cloud storage;

:Notify Admin via email and in-app notification;

:Display success confirmation to Seller;

stop
@enduml